<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ض ر م<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣١٢٥ - ض ر م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ضرِمَ يَضرَم، ضَرَمًا، فهو ضارِم وضَرِم<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ضرِمتِ النَّارُ:</span> اتَّقدت، اشتعلت، التهبت، اشتدّ حرُّها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ضرِم الشَّخصُ:</span> اشتدَّ غضبُه أو جوعُه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>